
--------------------
[--] Manage triggers - https://github.com/Verlihub/verlihub/wiki/Messages#file-triggers
--------------------
[-] !addtrigger <trigger> <params>  Add a new trigger
[-] !deltrigger <trigger>  Remove a trigger
[-] !htrigger  Show an help and available trigger flags
[-] !lsttrigger  List available triggers
[-] !modtrigger <trigger> <params>  Change a trigger 
--------------------
